{"tid":2370779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子不滿判決 法庭刺死法官","createTime":"2021-01-18T09:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T09:42:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8a2990b997d62d3aaf3c0e1b5e91f07ed2434a","tid":2370779,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"中國黑龍江省一名吳姓男子不滿離婚判決，對郝姓法官心生怨恨，竟攜帶尖刀在法庭刺死法官，今判決出爐，吳男因犯故意殺人罪，判處死刑，剝奪政治權利終身，附帶民事賠償65萬多元（約台幣281萬），令網友唏噓不已，紛紛直呼，「培養一個法官需要多少時間、多大精力，誰要跟他以命換命！」<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，吳男與妻子關女育有2名子女，關女於去年提起離婚訟訴，指出吳男時常對她實施家暴，夫妻感情已破裂，請求判決離婚，並對夫妻共同財產進行分割，此案當時由郝姓法官審理，檢視相關資料後，一審准予2人離婚，沒想到吳男對此相當不滿，酒後攜帶尖刀前往法庭理論，打傷對方後再狠刺胸口一刀，當場被公安人員抓獲，但郝姓法官因傷及肺動脈而失血過多，最終搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n該案判決結果今出爐，吳男因犯故意殺人罪，判處死刑，剝奪政治權利終身，附帶民事賠償65萬多元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3414467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3414467&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9T2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=6a5ef5a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3414467&h=0550a43c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3414467</a>"},{"pid":"76b8b0ec9c04d57c8f4da554af9ae57e443d7391","tid":2370779,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ef0ad7782b8d005fc6ba1a325e6b6ae1364a5b","tid":2370779,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ab7b51646189e33132fdfc929641657bf8e31e","tid":2370779,"uid":28613